  Stable on alpha.

  29 Jul 2004; Jeremy Huddleston <eradicator@gentoo.org>
  -sox-12.17.4-r1.ebuild:
  Removing insecure version.

*sox-12.17.4-r2 (29 Jul 2004)

  29 Jul 2004; Chris White <chriswhite@gentoo.org>
  +files/sox-wave-overflow.patch, +sox-12.17.4-r2.ebuild:
  Bumped to -r2 and added buffer overflow patch to address bug #57962.

  07 Jul 2004; Hardave Riar <hardave@gentoo.org> sox-12.17.4-r1.ebuild:
  Added ~mips KEYWORD and gnuconfig_update

  01 Jul 2004; Jeremy Huddleston <eradicator@gentoo.org>
  sox-12.17.3-r3.ebuild, sox-12.17.4-r1.ebuild:
  virtual/glibc -> virtual/libc

  19 Jun 2004; Jeremy Huddleston <eradicator@gentoo.org>
  sox-12.17.4-r1.ebuild:
  Added alsa-lib to DEPEND when USE=alsa.

  03 May 2004; Jeremy Huddleston <eradicator@gentoo.org>
  sox-12.17.4-r1.ebuild:
  Changing mad dep to madplay.

  20 Apr 2004; Jeremy Huddleston <eradicator@gentoo.org>
  sox-12.17.3-r3.ebuild:
  Added IUSE.

  11 Apr 2004; Jason Wever <weeve@gentoo.org> sox-12.17.4-r1.ebuild:
  Stable on sparc.

  01 Apr 2004; Jason Wever <weeve@gentoo.org> sox-12.17.4-r1.ebuild:
  Added ~sparc keyword.

  31 Mar 2004; Jeremy Huddleston <eradicator@gentoo.org>
  sox-12.17.3-r1.ebuild, sox-12.17.4-r1.ebuild, sox-12.17.4.ebuild:
  Stable on x86.  Removing old ebuilds.

